Backtracking

1) Identify stages (left/right)
2) Go stages one by one (like every i)
3) Explore choices (what u can do at each stage)
4) Make one choice and store somewhere
5) Go to next stage
6) Backtrack that is reverse decision
7) When all stages finished(like index == n)
8) whatever u have stored will be result

